overview.en: BBA is a blockchain-based digital asset artificial intelligence quantitative trading ecosystem. It captures the data of major exchanges around the world for trading, and can use high-frequency quantization by using different conversion channels, transaction currencies, and transaction depth. Trading strategies benefit from it.
overview.zh: BBA是基于区块链的数字资产人工智能量化交易生态系统，抓取全球各大交易所的数据进行交易刷单，利用换算通道、交易币种、交易深度之间的不同，可以使用高频量化交易策略从中获利。
